<DOCHDR>
http://www.npr.gov:80/library/direct/memos/2372.html 192.239.92.66 19970120001642 text/html 13419
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 00:17:12 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 13247
