<P>
<P>          BIBLIOGRAPHY<BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>          APPENDIX A -- POLICY DOCUMENTS<BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>            Executive Order No. 12862<BR>

<P>              &quot;Setting Custome rService Standards&quot;<BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>            OMB Memorandum M-93-14<BR>

<P>              &quot;Facilitating Customer Surveys&quot;<BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>          APPENDIX B -- SELECTED TECHNICAL NOTES<BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>            Introduction<BR>

