<P>an extensive bibliography of materials  on<BR>

<P>federalism in 1982.  [&quot;Federalism and<BR>

<P>Intergovernmental Relations: A Selected<BR>

<P>Bibliography,&quot;  Dalrymple, Helen, Congressional<BR>

<P>Research Service, August 2, 1982.]<BR>

