<HTML> 
<HEAD>
<TITLE>	Selected Links to Initiatives Related or Similar to the Oregon Option</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<P>
US Department of Education - Waivers granted through June, 1995: <A HREF="http://www.ed.gov/flexibility/9506-ltr.html">Letter from Richard Riley, Secretary of Education, on Flexibility and Waivers</A><BR>

<P>US Department of Education, <A HREF="http://www.ed.gov/flexibility/">Initiative on Flexibility and Waivers</A><BR>

<P>US Department of Health and Human Services, Administration for Children and Families, <A HREF="http://www.acf.dhhs.gov/ACFnews/news/welfaredemo">Welfare Reform Demonstrations</A>
<P>

